# DA-4: Change Boundary Rule
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: Class modification

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Business Responsibility: The domain-driven purpose of a class.

ENFORCE: A class may only change when its business responsibility changes.
PROHIBIT: Modifying implementation for technical convenience alone.
ON VIOLATION: Notify Change Impact Analyzer Skill; halt non-compliant changes.
